title: Headlight Bulb - Replacement

body.body: This model is fitted with light emitting diodes (LED) headlights. The headlights, DRL or LED position light are situated within the headlight assembly and are sealed, maintenance free LED units. The headlight unit must be replaced in the event of failure of the headlights, DRL or LED position lights.
